<div class="container">
    <h1>
        OER World Map
    </h1>
    <h2>
        This year we are going to map the world of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_educational_resources">OER</a>
    </h2>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="row">
            <div id="worldmap" style="width: 800px; height: 500px"></div>
            <table class="table" id="users_by_country">
                <script type="application/ld+json">
                    {{{countryAggregation}}}
                </script>
                {{#countryAggregation.entries}}
                <tr><td>{{key}}</td><td>{{value}}</td></tr>
                {{/countryAggregation.entries}}
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <p class="lead">
            Leave your address to be kept up to date or even get an active role in the process:
        </p>

        <div class="row register">
            <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                <a href="/user/" class="hijax transclude">Register</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <div class="section mission-statements" style="height: 200px;">
        <h2>
            Mission Statements
        </h2>
        <div class="vision-statements">
            {{#visionStatements}}
            <blockquote class="vision">
                <p>{{statement}}</p>
            </blockquote>
            {{/visionStatements}}
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <hr>
    
    <div class="section">
    	<h2>
            Country Champions
        </h2>
        <p>
        	We are looking for <strong>country champions</strong> who will help to map the OER world by country â€“ to gather data and spread the word.<br>
        	We currently have <strong>six</strong> country champions for the following countries:
        </p>
        <ul class="horizontal-list p">
        	<li class="label label-default">Brazil</li>
        	<li class="label label-default">Canada</li>
        	<li class="label label-default">Germany</li>
        	<li class="label label-default">Netherlands</li>
        	<li class="label label-default">Spain</li>
        	<li class="label label-default">United States</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="clear: both;">
        	Your's is not in the List? You are an OER pioneer? Let's talk!<br>
			Jan Neumann ist coordinating the country champions, best you drop him an email: <a href="mailto:neumann@hbz-nrw.de">neumann@hbz-nrw.de</a>
        </p>
    </div>
    
</div>
<script type="text/javascript" src="//cdn.jsdelivr.net/jquery.slick/1.4.0/slick.min.js"></script>
